text: Abdullah Al-Bahri (, born 16 March 1995) is a Saudi Arabian professional footballer who plays as a Goalkeeper for Pro League side Al-Ettifaq. ==Career== Al Bahri began his career at the youth team of Al-Ettifaq. On 16 June 2016, Al Bahri renews his contract with Al-Ettifaq for 5 year . On 17 August 2017, Al Bahri joined MS League side Al-Kawkab on loan for the 2017–18 season. On 21 January 2019, Al Bahri joined MS League side Abha on loan for the 2017–18 season. ==References== == External links == * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Saudi Arabian footballers Category:Saudi Arabia youth international footballers Category:Ettifaq FC players Category:Al-Kawkab FC players Category:Abha Club players Category:Saudi Professional League players Category:Prince Mohammad bin Salman League players Category:Association football goalkeepers
